  "detailed_description": "<h1>More games</h1><p><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://devdangames.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  ><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/706440/extras/devdangamesbanner.png?t=1523038005\" ></a></a></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/706440/extras/adventure.png?t=1523038005\" ><br>Battle your way and find a way to escape the invasion of <strong>cyborgs</strong> overwhelming military forces in a <strong>post-apocalyptic world</strong> ! Take advantage of the <strong>destructible buildings</strong> to ambush the cyborgs and <strong>eliminate their commanders</strong>.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/706440/extras/buggy.png?t=1523038005\" ><br><strong>Drive the buggy</strong> to explore the areas and collect dispersed items and weapons. Listen to radio communications to find out what happened.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/706440/extras/arenamode.png?t=1523038005\" ><br>Play the <strong><i>arena mode</i></strong> featuring 4 maps with <strong>boost bonus</strong> randomly appearing during the game which are giving <strong>high jumps, invulnerability, unlimited ammo, high speed</strong>, etc... to resist for as long as possible against waves of cyborgs.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/706440/extras/weapons.png?t=1523038005\" ><br>Powerful weapons such as <strong>automatic shotguns</strong>, <strong>laser rifles</strong> and <strong>assault rifles</strong> boostable with <strong>explosive ammo</strong> !<br><br><strong>17 achievements</strong> to unlock, with support of <strong>Steam cloud</strong> and customisable graphics settings, including support for <strong>4k resolution</strong> and playable with <strong>Xbox-like gamepads</strong>.",
  "about_the_game": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/706440/extras/adventure.png?t=1523038005\" ><br>Battle your way and find a way to escape the invasion of <strong>cyborgs</strong> overwhelming military forces in a <strong>post-apocalyptic world</strong> ! Take advantage of the <strong>destructible buildings</strong> to ambush the cyborgs and <strong>eliminate their commanders</strong>.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/706440/extras/buggy.png?t=1523038005\" ><br><strong>Drive the buggy</strong> to explore the areas and collect dispersed items and weapons. Listen to radio communications to find out what happened.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/706440/extras/arenamode.png?t=1523038005\" ><br>Play the <strong><i>arena mode</i></strong> featuring 4 maps with <strong>boost bonus</strong> randomly appearing during the game which are giving <strong>high jumps, invulnerability, unlimited ammo, high speed</strong>, etc... to resist for as long as possible against waves of cyborgs.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/706440/extras/weapons.png?t=1523038005\" ><br>Powerful weapons such as <strong>automatic shotguns</strong>, <strong>laser rifles</strong> and <strong>assault rifles</strong> boostable with <strong>explosive ammo</strong> !<br><br><strong>17 achievements</strong> to unlock, with support of <strong>Steam cloud</strong> and customisable graphics settings, including support for <strong>4k resolution</strong> and playable with <strong>Xbox-like gamepads</strong>.",
  "short_description": "Escape the invasion of cyborgs and explore the open world map with the buggy, find weapons and items, listen to radio communications, use the destructible buildings to ambush the cyborgs. Also featuring an arena mode !",
